<section id="about" class="py-20 container mx-auto px-4">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
    <div class="order-2 md:order-1 w-full md:w-1/2 mt-8 md:mt-0">
      <img
        src="/browser-about.svg"
        alt="Browser feature illustration"
        class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="order-1 md:order-2 w-full md:w-1/2">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
        About LBrowser
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          LBrowser is designed from the ground up to protect your privacy while delivering 
          exceptional performance. Unlike conventional browsers that track your every move, 
          we believe your data belongs to you and only you.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Built on open-source principles, our browser blocks trackers automatically, prevents 
          fingerprinting, and encrypts your connection whenever possible. The intuitive interface 
          puts you in control without sacrificing the features you love.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Whether you're a privacy advocate, a developer, or just someone who wants a faster 
          browsing experience, LBrowser offers the tools and technology to make the web work 
          for you, not against you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pt-16">
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">
    Features
  </h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
    <div class="flex-1 bg-white p-6 text-center rounded shadow-lg">
      <img
        src="/icons/privacy.svg"
        alt="Privacy Icon"
        class="mx-auto mb-4 w-12 h-12"
      />
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Total Privacy</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        Protect your data with built-in ad and tracker blocking, ensuring your online activity remains private.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 bg-white p-6 text-center rounded shadow-lg">
      <img
        src="/icons/speed.svg"
        alt="Speed Icon"
        class="mx-auto mb-4 w-12 h-12"
      />
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Lightning Speed</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        Experience faster browsing with optimized performance and reduced load times.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 bg-white p-6 text-center rounded shadow-lg">
      <img
        src="/icons/customization.svg"
        alt="Customization Icon"
        class="mx-auto mb-4 w-12 h-12"
      />
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Customizable Experience</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        Tailor your browsing experience with a variety of themes, extensions, and settings to suit your needs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>